  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt;=12% risk for post-operative ARF on our recently developed and validated prediction
             score for ARF after liver surgery, patients will need five points or more in the
             pre-operative assessment of the predictors to be enrolled in the trial

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  &lt; 18 years

          -  liver cirrhosis

          -  coronary insufficiency with ST-elevation or ST-depression in the - - intra-operative
             ECG as signs of an acute coronary syndrome

          -  pregnancy and breast feed
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
